dsDescriptionValue.value: This dataset contains responses to the ArchaeoGLOBE land use questionnaire collected between May 18 and July 31, summary tables including consensus assessments, and supplementary figures. All personal and identifying information has been removed.

keywordValue.value: Archaeology, Land Use, Agriculture, Pastoralism, Foraging, Hunting and Gathering
